Title: Comment on prescription problem in light-cone gauge

Authors: D.K.Park

Comments: 5 pages, Latex

Journal-ref: J.Korean Phys.Soc. 28 (1995) 793-795

Recently suggested causal principal value and causal prescriptions for the"spurious singularity" in light-cone gauge theories are nothing but thedifferent guises of usual Mandelstam-Leibbrandt prescription.